    "description": "■ 即使您从未玩过 RTS！ 或者即使你以前都玩过！<br>Tactics Greed 是一款休闲的甲板建筑动作 RTS 游戏。<br>游戏操作简便、规则简单、游戏时间短、角色可爱，即使从未玩过 RTS 的玩家也能轻松上手。<br>卡组建造和动作 RTS 的结合为那些已经玩过 RTS 游戏的玩家带来了全新的体验。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/869f90fd564bd4c0af6c6215cc604ba7.poster.avif?t=1721830082\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/869f90fd564bd4c0af6c6215cc604ba7.webm?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/869f90fd564bd4c0af6c6215cc604ba7.mp4?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>■ 在地牢中组建你的卡组。<br>攻打地下城，寻找卡片。<br>您可以获得各种同伴和魔法，包括作为盾牌的 &quot;骑士&quot;、作为攻击手的 &quot;魔法师 &quot;和从背后发射炸弹的 &quot;大型单位&quot;。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/055e3f3bc2c9b3c22ad8b73221ca73c6.poster.avif?t=1721830082\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/055e3f3bc2c9b3c22ad8b73221ca73c6.webm?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/055e3f3bc2c9b3c22ad8b73221ca73c6.mp4?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>■ 在竞技场挑战世界。<br>通过异步通信挑战世界排名。<br>您可以享受无压力的对战，无需 &quot;等待、作弊或苦恼&quot;。<br>排名者的行动模式会被重放，等待您的是堪比实时交流的激烈对战。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/017fddd8a64f61a9e75e5ea53e922edf.poster.avif?t=1721830082\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/017fddd8a64f61a9e75e5ea53e922edf.webm?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/017fddd8a64f61a9e75e5ea53e922edf.mp4?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>■ 双人合作和竞技游戏<br>与两名玩家一起游戏时，精彩和刺激更胜一筹。<br>在合作游戏中，高级玩家可以控制一名指挥官，而新手玩家则可以控制同伴的单位，让您与心爱的人一起游戏。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/9ee4560753d78b184f4398eb084040ab.poster.avif?t=1721830082\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/9ee4560753d78b184f4398eb084040ab.webm?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/9ee4560753d78b184f4398eb084040ab.mp4?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>*双人游戏需要两个游戏手柄。<br><br><br>■ 即使只用鼠标也能轻松上手。<br>睡前或工作休息时的小茶点。<br>左手拿杯子，右手拿鼠标。<br>贪婪战术》出现在显示器的末端。<br>在最佳的放松时间里，来一款超棒的 RTS 怎么样？<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/e9c877796b49f5dcdae75c69e1f893e9.poster.avif?t=1721830082\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/e9c877796b49f5dcdae75c69e1f893e9.webm?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265190/extras/e9c877796b49f5dcdae75c69e1f893e9.mp4?t=1721830082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
